OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUniversal credit switchover
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fis a bad move, say         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcharities                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Plans to forcibly move millions of     
OL,6, people off legacy benefits and onto    
OL,7, universal credit begin on Monday, amid 
OL,8, calls for the process to be halted.    
OL,10,FSome 2.6 million claimants will begin  
OL,11,Fto receive letters urging them to apply
OL,12,Ffor universal credit.                  
OL,14,FBut leading charities warn the enforced
OL,15,Fswitchover could leave some vulnerable 
OL,16,Fpeople "unable to pay their bills".    
OL,18,FMinisters insist the move to "a benefit
OL,19,Fsystem suited to the 21st century" will
OL,20,Fbe "carefully managed".                
